"This sheet falls within NA 38-5, 1501, 1:250,000 and NA 38-049, Y630, 1:100,000." "NIMA REF. NO. Y921XBAARDHEERE." "NSN 7643014033646." "This map is red-light readable." Includes auxillary glossary, Somalia location map, and boundary index.
